#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: lzm-lead-button.php
msgid "LZM Lead Button"
msgstr "LZM Lead Button"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: lzm-lead-button.php
msgid "https://github.com/valeriagoncalez/lzm-lead-button"
msgstr "https://github.com/valeriagoncalez/lzm-lead-button"

#. Description of the plugin
#: lzm-lead-button.php
msgid ""
"Prevent accidental clicks. Add a confirmation form before opening WhatsApp "
"to ensure only real leads are counted."
msgstr ""
"Evite cliques acidentais. Adicione um formulário de confirmação antes de "
"abrir o WhatsApp e garanta que apenas leads reais sejam contados."

